Scheduled Guests

From the Infowars web site ::

Alex talks with the president and founder of the American Small Business League, Lloyd Chapman, about the Occupy Wall Street protests now entering a third week. Mr. Chapman and Jones will also talk about the economy and how Obama's policies are hurting small business in America. 

In addition to covering the latest breaking news, Alex will talk about the Occupy Wall Street movement and how it is being undermined and sold out by establishment Democrats and the globalists.
